{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two different game modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survivor</strong> (arcade)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story Campaign</strong> (rts)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each mode with unique gameplay and content, but with connected storyline and characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>-= Survivor Mode =-</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Huge hordes of enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Awesome weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Unlimited upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Base of operations on a spaceship Big Fish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Lots of fun tasks to finish (achievements)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Cool characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Story presented in Visual Novel style - with great writing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Play as Operator - an independent agent operating on the fringes of known space, looking to make profit</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>-= Story Campaign =-</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Command troops in real-time combat with dozens of units on screen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Explore the map to find new allies, resources, and secrets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Capture production points</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Destroy enemy bases</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Participate in an epic space-opera story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Ultra-casual controls - can play with a single gamepad stick!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Play as Soldier - who was abandoned by the military command on an alien planet and who has to take the command in his own hands to escape the war and save his life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay mechanics in Story Campaign mode:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Allies will automatically follow the player and attack enemies in range. The player's primary job is to gather a large force of allied troops, and then defeat enemy troops by tactically balancing his own position in a way that protects his allies from harm while also keeping himself alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game length: 10+ hours in Survivor mode and 3+ hours in Story Campaign mode.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738093870","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822570/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738093870","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822570/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738093870","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822570/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738093870","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two different game modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survivor</strong> (arcade)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story Campaign</strong> (rts)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each mode with unique gameplay and content, but with connected storyline and characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>-= Survivor Mode =-</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Huge hordes of enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Awesome weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Unlimited upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Base of operations on a spaceship Big Fish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Lots of fun tasks to finish (achievements)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Cool characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Story presented in Visual 